              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "ACTIV"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Irradiated for 180 to 342 min by 0.23 to",
                " 1.31 uA current."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "XSPEC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " After cooling for ~20 min, the irradiated",
                " targets were installed inside the PIXE chamber,",
                " and X-ray spectra were collected up to 170 hrs."
